title: Jeff Garlin
itunes:title: Jeff Garlin
itunes:subtitle: JEFF GARLIN (Curb Your Enthusiasm, The Goldbergs, Toy Story 3&4, ParaNorman, Wall-E, Arrested Development) joins Anna to discuss taking yourself too seriously, how to nap, stupid decisions, dating after divorce, stand-up, Coco the Clown and more. Anna and
description:

- Ham vs. peanut butter sandwiches

- Stupid decisions
- The Me Too movement vs. hugs
